Purpose: Small software tools for use with RFA

----------------------------------------------------

1a. Demonstration of AM demodulation, input: mono WAV file:
	basic_am_demod.py
	Usage: python basic_am_demod.py <monowavfile.wav>
	Output: PNG of signal processing visualisation
1b. Calibration demo input for basic_am_demod.py:
	sine-200x5x6.wav
1c. Speech demo input for basic_am_demod.py:
	one-to-thirty-2044_04_22_11s_16k.wav

2.a Demonstration of FM demodulation method, input: mono WAV file
	Usage: PyADMF.py wavfilename high|fairlyhigh|mid|fairlylow|low single|multiple
	Output: visualisation of steps in AMDF demodulation
2.b Demonstration of FM demodulation: input: mono WAV file
	Usage: ./basic_fm_demod.py wavfilename high|fairlyhigh|mid|fairlylow|low

